body.description: The lightweight Graco SnugRide 35 Lite LX Infant Car Seat supports baby in comfort from 4-35 lb and up to 32". The infant car seat weighs just 7.2 lb, making it easy to carry baby from car to stroller. The 4-position adjustable base with level indicator ensures an accurate install. The two-piece infant head and body supports keep baby snug and comfortable as he or she grows. The SnugRide 35 Lite LX car seat installs easily using the vehicle seat belt or LATCH. It features a rotating canopy to keep baby comfortable and shaded in all environments. Create a travel system for your infant, or use this car seat in multiple cars: SnugRide 35 Lite LX attaches with a one-step secure connection to Graco strollers and infant car seat bases. The car seat is Graco ProtectPlus Engineered to help protect in frontal, side, rear, and rollover crashes.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars as always Grsco delivers.
reviews.reviewText: The car seat is wonderful. It is the perfect size and light wight which makes it easy to pick up. This is for a newborn so it’s easy to install and will work perfectly with the stroller attachment. Would highly recommend for anyone who wants a light weight car seat.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent car seat, easy to install!
reviews.reviewText: We use this car seat for our newborn and now, and it has been a blessing! It’s gentle on our baby’s back as it has soft materials on its surface, and the positioning and curve of the seat base is comfortable for our baby. Only flaw would be the canopy is flimsy and we wish it came with a visor of some sort to keep it standing and out of our baby’s face. Outside that, it’s a great car seat and securely fastens into the car. The clips also easily close and don’t cause strain to our baby.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Car Seat for Great Price
reviews.reviewText: This car seat was used with my 3 year old when she was born and I have purchased it again for our second who is due soon. I absolutely loved this car seat. It’s light and easy to carry. It does get a little uncomfortable to carry as baby gets heavier, but that’s expected. It was very easy to install the base and to connect and disconnect the seat from the base, but hard for me to uninstall the base after it’s tightened, but I do have that issue with any base. It has so many uses as well. We loved that you can remove the car seat from the base and also the fact that I was able to attach the seat to my stroller from Graco. This car seat was used on so many car rides and twice as many walks. We were able to use it for a good long while with my daughter and only stopped use once she got too big. I didn’t have any regrets on not getting a more expensive seat, this fit all our needs. Definitely recommend this seat, especially at the price! You won’t regret it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Bought this as a shower gift for my nephew. This was on their wish list. I found it easily on Amazon. When he took it out of the box I was very pleased with the quality and how lightweight the seat is to carry. Grace has always put out good quality products.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Lightweight but latches get stuck every time
reviews.reviewText: The car seat fits our newborn well, is very lightweight, and easy to adjust the straps. The issue we have is it is HORRIBLE to remove from the base. The clips always catch and we have to fight to get it to disconnect. This really sucks in winter when we try to get our daughter in the house as fast as possible. Now, I just stay home with her whenever it's not necessary for us to go somewhere to avoid the fight.
